{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"showsUserLocation"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Setting this property to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":" causes the map view to use the Core Location"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"framework to find the current location. As long as this property is "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"type":"text","text":", the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map view continues to track the user’s location and update it periodically."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This property does not indicate whether the user’s position is actually visible"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"on the map, only whether the map view is allowed to display it. To determine"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"whether the user’s position is visible, use the "},{"code":"userLocationVisible","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The default value of this property is "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Your app must specify a value for "},{"code":"NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" in its "},{"code":"Info.plist","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to satisfy the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"requirements of the underlying Core Location framework when enabling this"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you implement a custom location manager, set the ","type":"text"},{"code":"locationManager","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" before","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"calling ","type":"text"},{"code":"showsUserLocation","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview\/showsuserlocation"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"]]},"metadata":{"remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapView.h#L590","fileName":"MLNMapView.h"},"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView(py)showsUserLocation","title":"showsUserLocation","roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"property","fragments":[{"text":"showsUserLocation","kind":"identifier"}]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the map may display the user location."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView\/showsUserLocation","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit wi